#H bit | arpStat | Description
#H =============================================================================
     0 | 0x01    | ARP detected
#I   1 | 0x02    | Gratuitous ARP (sender IP same as target IP)
#I   2 | 0x04    | ARP Probe
#I   3 | 0x08    | ARP Announcement

     4 | 0x10    | -
#W   5 | 0x20    | MAC/IP list truncated... increase ARP_MAX_IP
     6 | 0x40    | -
#W   7 | 0x80    | ARP spoofing (same MAC assigned to multiple IPs)
